data.description: Assumable 3.25% interest rate available! UPGRADES GALORE: solar panels (paid off), a newer drain field and septic system, metal roof, updated interior painting, and a new A/C system and duct work- done! Welcome to Kingsland Country Estates nestled in the heart of Ocala with NO HOA or CDD. You will want to visit this home in person to see all that it has to offer, a perfect blend of country and close to enough to the city! This home sits on an expansive lot spanning almost half an acre, offering a tranquil retreat in a quiet neighborhood. It features 4 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, including two master bedrooms, perfect for multi-generational living or accommodating guests with utmost comfort and privacy. If you are looking for something for the whole family to enjoy, this is what you're looking for! Dive into relaxation in the sparkling pool, surrounded by a fenced yard that provides a secure space for your family and pets to roam freely. The updated kitchen features granite countertops and Samsung appliances. Need a separate space for entertainment or work? Look no further! This home offers a bonus game room or office area, providing the flexibility to customize the room to suit your needs. Parking is a breeze with the detached 2-car garage, offering ample space for vehicles and additional storage. The home also includes an extra outdoor building space that may be used as an efficiency or separate suite that has electricity and water already equipped. Enjoy the peace and privacy of a cul-de-sac location in a serene neighborhood, where you can unwind and escape the hustle and bustle of city life. Close to parks and trails as well as shopping conveniences! Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this extraordinary property! Contact us today to schedule a showing today.
